       id="session">
   <title>Session</title>
   <description>APIs that operate on sessions</description>
   <introduction>
      <paragraph>Session resources enable administration of user sessions. 
The following table lists the session resources:</paragraph>
      <table>
         <header>
            <row>
               <entry>HTTP Method</entry>
               <entry>URI pattern</entry>
               <entry>Description</entry>
            </row>
         </header>
         <body>
            <row>
               <entry>
                  <code>GET</code>
               </entry>
               <entry>
                  <code>/{db}/_session/{session-id}</code>
               </entry>
               <entry>Retrieves information about a session</entry>
            </row>
            <row>
               <entry>
                  <code>POST</code>
               </entry>
               <entry>
                  <code>/{db}/_session</code>
               </entry>
               <entry>Creates a session</entry>
            </row>
            <row>
               <entry>
                  <code>DELETE</code>
               </entry>
               <entry>
                  <code>/{db}/_session/{session-id}</code>
               </entry>
               <entry>Deletes a session</entry>
            </row>
            <row>
               <entry>
                  <code>DELETE</code>
               </entry>
               <entry>
                  <code>/{db}/_user/{name}/_session/{session-id}</code>
               </entry>
               <entry>Deletes a session for the specified user</entry>
            </row>
            <row>
               <entry>
                  <code>DELETE</code>
               </entry>
               <entry>
                  <code>/{db}/_user/{name}/_session</code>
               </entry>
               <entry>Deletes all sessions for the specified user</entry>
            </row>
         </body>
      </table>
      <paragraph>The following table defines the parameters used in the URI patterns:</paragraph>
         <table>
            <header>
               <row>
                  <entry>Name</entry>
                  <entry>Description</entry>
               </row>
            </header>
            <body>
               <row>
                  <entry>
                     <code>db</code>
                  </entry>
                  <entry>Name of the database</entry>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <entry>
                     <code>name</code>
                  </entry>
                  <entry>User name</entry>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <entry>
                     <code>session-id</code>
                  </entry>
                  <entry>Session ID</entry>
               </row>
            </body>
         </table>
   </introduction>
